Title: Love is in the Air
Description:
Smell these roses! My partner got them for me at the Gala of Gifts.

Interested in seeing things yourself? Head to the gates of Stormwind. There are gifts, and food, and you should taste the chocolate, it's delicious!
ObjectivesText: Visit the Gala of Gifts at the gates of Stormwind.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Speak with Luciana Delgado at the Gala of Gifts.

Objectives.Text: Portal taken to the Gala of Gifts
